OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud and
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain and drizzle across
OL,7,FOrkney this evening gradually
OL,8,Fextending across Shetland during the
OL,9,Fearly hours. Becoming misty with fog
OL,10,Fpatches. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FMisty start with some
OL,13,Fdrizzly rain, fog patches for
OL,14,FShetland. Otherwise a cloudy day with
OL,15,Foccasional light rain and some
OL,16,Fafternoon fog patches, but some drier
OL,17,Fweather too at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
