OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FMostly dry although rather cloudy on
OL,7,FThursday. Quite cloudy again on Friday
OL,8,Fwith some outbreaks of rain, perhaps
OL,9,Fdrier later. Largely dry with bright
OL,10,Fspells and variable cloud on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
